<br />
<br />Actually, cheating a bit with DPC+ Food Fight could be back-ported to the Atari 2600.  The graphics would have to be re-worked to only use one color per line but would be pretty similar.  This is one instance where software collision would be needed as the Chefs and items would all share sprite 1.

		

